high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the sofa on your right.
Pick up key chain from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the dresser.
Place key chain on the dresser.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the bed.
Pick up key chain from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the dresser.
Place key chain on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collecting key chain from different places and arranging them on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the safe.

Place key chain on the dresser.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the bed on your right.

high_descs: Turn left then turn right to walk through the passage and turn right after crossing the passage to find the safe.
Open the keychain and take out the keys from it and close it.
Turn around and then turn right to find the dresser.
Place the keychain on top of the dresser.

Pick up the keychain from the bed.
Turn right two times to reach the dresser.
Place the keychain on top of the dresser.
